---
---

<article class="card-base dashboard-panel">
	<div class="dashboard-panel-head">
		<div>
			<p class="dashboard-panel-eyebrow">说明</p>
			<h3 class="dashboard-panel-title">当前内容结构约定</h3>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="dashboard-guide-grid">
		<div class="dashboard-guide-card">
			<p class="dashboard-guide-title">长文放 `posts`</p>
			<p class="dashboard-guide-copy">题解、复盘、系统化总结继续进入文章流，并参与首页分页。</p>
		</div>
		<div class="dashboard-guide-card">
			<p class="dashboard-guide-title">短内容放 `notes`</p>
			<p class="dashboard-guide-copy">命令片段、调试记录、临时备忘单独成流，避免和长文混在一起。</p>
		</div>
		<div class="dashboard-guide-card">
			<p class="dashboard-guide-title">分类用一级 + 路径</p>
			<p class="dashboard-guide-copy">`category` 表示一级分类，`categoryPath` 补足下级路径，`series` 负责系列聚合。</p>
		</div>
		<div class="dashboard-guide-card">
			<p class="dashboard-guide-title">资源跟内容同目录</p>
			<p class="dashboard-guide-copy">新内容默认使用 `slug/index.md` 目录式结构，图片和附件跟着 slug 走。</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</article>
